  "html": "<!doctype html>\n<html lang=\"pt-BR\"><head>\n  <meta charset=\"utf-8\">\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\">\n  <title>Hub de Atas | Ata 002</title>\n  <style>\n    :root {\n      --bg: #f7f7f5;\n      --card: #ffffff;\n      --text: #1f2328;\n      --muted: #5f6b7a;\n      --line: #e7e8ea;\n      --accent: #0f766e;\n      --accent-soft: #ecfdf5;\n      --shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);\n      --radius: 14px;\n    }\n    * { box-sizing: border-box; }\n    body {\n      margin: 0;\n      font-family: \"Avenir Next\", \"Segoe UI\", \"Helvetica Neue\", sans-serif;\n      background:\n        radial-gradient(1200px 500px at 0% -10%, #eefaf8 0%, transparent 50%),\n        radial-gradient(900px 420px at 100% 0%, #f3f6ff 0%, transparent 55%),\n        var(--bg);\n      color: var(--text);\n      line-height: 1.55;\n    }\n    .wrap { width: min(1060px, 92vw); margin: 36px auto 56px; }\n    .hero {\n      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f766e 0%, #115e59 58%, #0a4f4a 100%);\n      color: #fff;\n      border-radius: var(--radius);\n      box-shadow: var(--shadow);\n      padding: 28px;\n      margin-bottom: 22px;\n    }\n    .hero h1 { margin: 0 0 10px; font-size: clamp(1.25rem, 2.1vw, 1.8rem); line-height: 1.2; }\n    .meta { display: flex; gap: 12px; flex-wrap: wrap; color: #dff5f3; font-size: 0.95rem; }\n    .meta span { background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12); border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2); border-radius: 999px; padding: 6px 12px; }\n    .hero-links { display: flex; gap: 10px; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-top: 12px; }\n    .hero-links a { color: #dff5f3; text-decoration: none; border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.25); border-radius: 999px; padding: 6px 12px; font-size: 0.88rem; background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08); }\n    .hero-links a:hover { background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.16); }\n    .card { background: var(--card); border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: var(--radius); box-shadow: var(--shadow); margin-bottom: 16px; overflow: hidden; }\n    .card-head { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; gap: 10px; padding: 16px 18px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line); background: #fcfcfc; }\n    .card-head h2 { margin: 0; font-size: 1.03rem; line-height: 1.3; }\n    .head-actions { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; flex-wrap: wrap; }\n    .btn { border: 1px solid #c8d6d5; background: #fff; color: #134e4a; border-radius: 999px; font-size: 0.84rem; padding: 8px 12px; cursor: pointer; transition: .15s ease; text-decoration:none; }\n    .btn:hover { background: var(--accent-soft); }\n    .content { padding: 18px; }\n    pre { margin: 0; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: break-word; font: 0.92rem/1.56 \"SF Mono\", Menlo, Consolas, monospace; color: #2a3138; }\n    table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.93rem; }\n    th, td { border: 1px solid var(--line); padding: 10px; vertical-align: top; text-align: left; }\n    th { background: #f8fafb; font-weight: 600; }\n    .muted { color: var(--muted); }\n    @media (max-width: 800px) {\n      .card-head { align-items: flex-start; flex-direction: column; }\n      .head-actions { width: 100%; }\n      .btn { width: fit-content; }\n    }\n  </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n  <main class=\"wrap\">\n    <section class=\"hero\">\n      <h1>Hub de Atas do Escritório No Azul</h1>\n      <div class=\"meta\">\n        <span>Ata atual: 002</span>\n        <span>Empresa: Escritório No Azul</span>\n        <span>Data da ata: 06/03/2026</span>\n        <span>Participantes: Layene Oliveira &amp; Thiago (Skala Lançamentos) e Viviane &amp; Alencar (Lube Digital)</span>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"hero-links\">\n        <a href=\"../../../index.html\">Ir para Hub</a>\n        <a href=\"../../../catalogo.html\">Abrir catálogo</a>\n        <a href=\"../../../editar-ata.html?slug=ata-002-reuniao-de-revisao-dos-produtos\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Editar ata</a>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"card\" id=\"bloco-1\">\n      <header class=\"card-head\">\n        <h2>Bloco 1 • Pauta da reunião (base)</h2>\n        <div class=\"head-actions\">\n          <button class=\"btn\" data-target=\"content-1\">Recolher conteúdo</button>\n        </div>\n      </header>\n      <div class=\"content\" id=\"content-1\">\n<pre>Título da reunião: Reunião de Revisão dos produtos\nData: 2026-03-06\nParticipantes: Layene Oliveira &amp; Thiago (Skala Lançamentos) e Viviane &amp; Alencar (Lube Digital)\n\nPontos de pauta previstos:\n1) Escopo e Precificação dos produtos\n2)\n3)\n4)\n\nDecisões tomadas:\n-\n\nPendências abertas:\n-\n\nPróxima data sugerida de retorno:\n-</pre>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"card\" id=\"bloco-2\">\n      <header class=\"card-head\">\n        <h2>Bloco 2 • Registro da call (anotações/transcrição)</h2>\n        <div class=\"head-actions\">\n          <button class=\"btn\" data-target=\"content-2\">Recolher conteúdo</button>\n        </div>\n      </header>\n      <div class=\"content\" id=\"content-2\">\n<pre>Preencher com os registros da reunião:\n- resumo\n- tópicos discutidos\n- pontos sensíveis\n- próximos passos objetivos</pre>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"card\" id=\"bloco-3\">\n      <header class=\"card-head\">\n        <h2>Bloco 3 • Compilação objetiva dos principais pontos discutidos</h2>\n        <div class=\"head-actions\">\n          <button class=\"btn\" data-target=\"content-3\">Recolher conteúdo</button>\n        </div>\n      </header>\n      <div class=\"content\" id=\"content-3\">\n        <table>\n          <thead>\n            <tr>\n              <th>Assunto da pauta</th>\n              <th>Ponto de vista Lube</th>\n              <th>Ponto de vista Skala</th>\n              <th>Ação principal</th>\n              <th>Responsável</th>\n              <th>Status</th>\n              <th>Janela da call</th>\n              <th>Data de retorno</th>\n            </tr>\n          </thead>\n          <tbody><tr><td>Escopo e Precificação dos produtos</td><td>Concordaram</td><td>Eles que apresentaram a proposta</td><td>Revisar apresentações e adequar criativos</td><td>Todos</td><td>Aprovado</td><td>N/A</td><td>N/A</td></tr></tbody>\n        </table>\n        <p class=\"muted\" style=\"margin:12px 0 0;\">O acompanhamento contínuo (FUP dia a dia) está centralizado no Hub.</p>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"card\">\n      <header class=\"card-head\">\n        <h2>Acompanhamento Contínuo</h2>\n        <div class=\"head-actions\">\n          <a class=\"btn\" href=\"../../../index.html\">Abrir Hub</a>\n        </div>\n      </header>\n      <div class=\"content\">\n        <p class=\"muted\" style=\"margin:0;\">Use o Painel FUP Central do Hub para registrar retornos do dia a dia entre as reuniões.</p>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n  </main>\n\n  <script>\n    const buttons = document.querySelectorAll('.btn[data-target]');\n    buttons.forEach((btn) => {\n      btn.addEventListener('click', () => {\n        const id = btn.getAttribute('data-target');\n        const el = document.getElementById(id);\n        if (!el) return;\n        const hidden = el.style.display === 'none';\n        el.style.display = hidden ? '' : 'none';\n        btn.textContent = hidden ? 'Recolher conteúdo' : 'Expandir conteúdo';\n      });\n    });\n  </script>\n\n\n</body></html>",
  "titulo": "Ata 002 • Reunião de Revisão dos produtos"
